      "settings": {
        "enable_dark": false,
        "subheading": "<p><strong>Sapphires</strong></p>",
        "title": "<p>A Stone of Depth, Strength & Individuality</p>",
        "description": "<p>Sapphires have long been revered for their beauty and symbolism. Known for their durability and depth of colour, they are a stone often chosen to mark meaningful moments - designed to be worn every day, and treasured for a lifetime.</p>",
        "feature_text": "<p>While most commonly associated with rich blue hues, sapphires exist in a wide spectrum of colours, each with its own unique character.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
