        "subheading": "",
        "title": "<p><em>Australian Sapphires</em></p>",
        "description": "<p>At Natalie Marie Jewellery, we are proud to offer <strong>Australian origin sapphires</strong>, sourced primarily from Queensland’s gem fields.</p><p>These stones are known for their:</p><ul><li>Rich, moody colour palette</li><li>Distinctive teal and parti tones (not necessarily what we offer online- but only bespoke)</li><li>Natural variation and depth</li></ul><p></p><p>Australian sapphires offer a level of <strong>traceability and transparency</strong> that is not always possible within the global gemstone market, allowing us to share a clearer understanding of their origin and journey.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
    },
