        "media_width": "6",
        "content_position": "topLeftSticky",
        "subheading": "",
        "title": "<p><em>Sourcing & Transparency</em></p>",
        "description": "<p>The global gemstone industry is complex, with many stones passing through multiple hands before reaching a jeweller.</p><p>At NMJ, we take a considered approach to sourcing:</p><ul><li>We work with <strong>trusted suppliers and long-term partners</strong></li><li>We prioritise stones where <strong>origin can be verified</strong></li><li>We seek to collaborate with suppliers who support</li><li> responsible environmental practices</li><li>fair working conditions</li><li>community investment</li></ul><p>Where a stone is sold with an origin claim, we ensure this is supported by documented evidence of provenance from the supplier.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
    },
