        "media_width": "6",
        "content_position": "topLeftSticky",
        "subheading": "",
        "title": "<p><em>Custom Cut Stones</em></p>",
        "description": "<p>Many of the sapphires we offer are custom cut specifically for our designs, allowing us to:</p><ul><li>Highlight the natural beauty of each stone</li><li>Maximise colour and light performance</li><li>Create pieces that feel considered and intentional</li></ul><p>We work with specialised cutters who understand how to reveal the unique characteristics within each individual gemstone.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
