        "subheading": "",
        "title": "<p>Our Perspective</p>",
        "description": "<p>We are drawn to sapphires for their quiet strength and individuality.</p><p>Our sapphires are ethically sourced from Australia, celebrated for their exceptional quality, rich natural colour, and traceable origin.</p><p>Each stone carries a sense of depth - formed over time, shaped by nature, and chosen with intention.</p><p>Whether selected for its colour, origin, or meaning, a sapphire offers something deeply personal:</p><p>a piece that feels entirely your own.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
